node.text: Hayes Hunter Verstuyft • Feb 4 2020 •  8 lbs 13 oz • 22 inches
My heart might explode. Welcome to our wolf pack, Hayes Hunter Verstuyft. We love you so much.

🎶 They’re the 3 best friends that anybody could have 🎶 HAPPY BIRTHDAY MONICA!! 3 of my besties were all born within 3 days of eachother... and today they are 33! I must have some kind of awesome vibe with Aquarius babies and I’m so excited I’m about to have one of my very own. These girls mean so much to me... love y’all a million. @handcraftyoga @cojo1987 @cwyatt21
Happy Birthday to this angel. Love you so much @cwyatt21 we will be friends til we are old and senile... then we’ll be NEW friends. 😂♥️
Happy Birthday to this gem of a best friend. LYLAS BETCH. @cojo1987
You may not have a name yet, but you have a room!! 2 more weeks and our sweet little guy will be here! @46ranch
2019 was a great year. We slowed it down, enjoyed focusing on our little growing family... this was by far my favorite moment last year. We can’t wait for all 2020 has in store for us!
Cody rocks. Had so much fun today hosting Lyrics class holiday party! Snowballs and Snowcones! #bestdadever #iloveyou #lyriclane #christmas @46ranch

What a magical night celebrating this sweet baby coming!! My friends have outdone themselves again spoiling me and this baby rotten! Thank you so much @cwyatt21 @cojo1987 @leighcurry for such a great night! I am so blessed by your love and friendship.
Technology is cray. Looks like I’m having Lyrics twin. 7 more weeks and we get to meet this sweet little babe. 💙
Spreading that Christmas cheer! #jordanlanedesigns #merrychristmas
Our little 46-rancher finally joined the big boy buck club. Big day for little man Lyric! Reppin that @buckdoestx camo. @46ranch #firstbuck #littleman #family #lyriclane

Happy Anniversary to my partner in crime. 9 years has flown by with you.  Doing life and makin babies with my best friend is such a blessing. I love you more every time I get to wake up next to ya! Let’s keep going. ♥️🥰😘😘 @46ranch

Happy Sons Day to my little man. An easy excuse to express my unconditional, over the moon kind of love for you! God blessed me with the silliest, most kind, smart, and handsome little fella. I Thank him for you everyday. Can’t wait to see you be a big brother! #lyriclane
Happy Birthday Jake!! My Bestie since I was 3 years old! Love you lots, cherish all our silly memories more than you know!!! Here’s to 29!! 🍻
Baby Boy #2 coming soon! 💙 @46ranch
Just got this pic from Lyrics teacher. He is easy to spot. 😂 #Lyriclane #2ndgrade 🤘🏼

Love you to the moon, kid. Praying for the safety and happiness of all the babes going back to school today. #lyriclane #secondgrade
